        FieldNames getParametricValues(Collection<String> fieldNames,
                             Collection<ResourceIdentifier> indexes,
                             GetParametricValuesRequestBuilder params)
                               throws HodErrorException
        Query parametric values for the fieldName using a token proxy provided by a TokenProxyService
        Parameters:
        fieldNames - A list of field names to return values for
        indexes - The indexes to get values from
        params - Additional parameters to be sent as part of the request
        Returns:
        A list of field names with their parametric values
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If a TokenProxyService has not been defined
        HodAuthenticationFailedException - If the token associated with the token proxy has expired
        HodErrorException
